subproject.description:
This project is part of the LDC-SIDS Portfolio Project for mSustainable Land Management and will contribute to achive the objectives of Operational Programme 15 and Strategic Priority 1 related to Trageted Capacity Building for SLM with 4 key expected outcomes : 
- Capacity of communities and institutions strenghned; 
- Land degradation issues mainstreamed into policies and programs for poverty alleviation and sustainable development;
- A Mid-Term Investment and Resource Mobilization Plan for SLM implemented;
- A funcional Management Unit and adaptive lessons implemented.

